      "type": "text",
      "content": "Your social life is defined as the activities you do with other people for pleasure, when you are not working. It's important to have a social life, but what's right for one person won't be right for another. Some of us feel energised by spending lots of time with others,\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 1
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​, some of us may feel drained, even if it's doing something we enjoy. This is why finding a\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 2
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nin your social life is key. Spending too much time on your own, not\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 3
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nothers, can make you feel lonely and\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 4
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​. Loneliness is known to impact on your mental health and\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 5
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\na low mood. Anyone can feel lonely at any time. This might be especially true if,\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 6
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nyou are working from home and you are\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 7
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\non the usual social conversations that happen in an office. Other life changes can\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 8
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nperiods of loneliness too, such as retirement changing jobs or becoming a parent. It's important to recognise these feelings of loneliness. There are ways to\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 9
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\na social life, but it can feel overwhelming\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 10
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​. It's a great ideal to start by thinking about hobbies you enjoy. You can them find groups and activities related to those where you will be able to meet\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 11
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\npeople. There are groups aimed at new parents at those who want to\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 12
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\na new sport for the first time, or networking events for those in the same profession to meet up and\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 13
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nideas. On the other hand, it's\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 14
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\npossible to have too much of a social life. If you feel like you're always doing something and there is never any\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 15
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nin your calendar for downtime, you could suffer social burnout or social\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 16
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​. We all have our own social limit and it's important to recognise when you're feeling like it's all too much. Low mood, low energy, irritability and trouble sleeping could all be\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 17
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nof poor social health. Make sure you\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 18
    },
    {
